This paper discusses the expansion of question answering tasks and datasets, which are commonly found in natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning (ML) research. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which focuses on NLP research. The paper also touches on AI and ML, which makes cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) likely sub-categories as well. Additionally, the paper mentions image and video understanding, which falls under cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper discusses the definition and utility of question answering, which could also fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
